Document package
========================================================
Create a new `R/package_name.R` file
```{r, eval = FALSE}
#' greetings
#'
#' @description A package that provides a pleasant way to say hello or goodbye to a friend.
#'
#' @section greetings functions:
#' say_aloha
#'
"_PACKAGE"
```

```{r eval = FALSE}
